{"tid":1693873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈需要你嘅支持 [2日得79個人支持，WTF]","createTime":"2019-11-05T00:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T14:41:05.000Z","uid":179231,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4954e8f2075d9e2b72a6b186c65d4619b868cc64","tid":1693873,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:33:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">[之前開咗創意台，轉開一個吹水台，懇求大家唔Like都幫手推一下] </span><br />\n<br />\n我只係一個全職OL，只敢行向中間，驚死無用(但絕對唔會一放TG就奔跑，求下大家唔好再奔跑好嘛？)<br />\n<br />\n我一直都整開手作仔，去香港手作展都見到好多香港人係做手作搵食，但香港手作永遠都好似只可以係興趣咁，點解唔可以係搵食? 明明大家見到香港文宣都做得好靚&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n成立黃色經濟圈係我近排不同諗有咩可以做到，錢我唔多亦唔係做開生意。但每個月再慳D, 幾千我都可以afford 到，我相信有心就可以，一步一步黎。<br />\n<br />\n所以我開咗個page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HandcraftStation-108398293936563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHandcraftStation-108398293936563&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=3a443b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HandcraftStation-108398293936563</a><br />\n<br />\n第一步: 我需要得到你哋嘅like，請like個page<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">(11月5日Update: 2日得79個人Like，唔好咁啦~)</span> <br />\n第二步: 如果你係手作人又同意我個諗法，可以請你inbox我嘛？未需要即刻決定寄賣，但我想得到你哋嘅意見<br />\n第三步: 當有手作人回覆我之後，我會自己出錢整個online shop <br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">(11月5日Update: 已經Setup緊，應該呢個星期內完成)，大家可以上網買。</span><br />\n<br />\n而手作人嘅成品係會將成品寄存向一個點集合寄出(我計過我可以負擔到一個月3000蚊租去做呢樣嘢，)<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">(11月5日Update: 搵咗D舖都有d out budget，大家有介紹請通知🙏)</span><br />\n<br />\n我未諗到點收手作人錢，抽成?義賣?大家歡迎比意見&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">(11月5日Update: 呢2日都得到幾位手作人聯絡，初步應該都係諗住抽成10%，扣咗交易費，就會係盈利)</span><br />\n<br />\nDefaults唔使講，50%盈利會捐到星火，50%會去支持黃色經濟圈(可能全買光時禮品卡之後捐比有需要人士)<br />\n<br />\n首先，請大家一點支持，Like個Page同<br />\nshare比你識嘅手作人知🙏"},{"pid":"5a258469e9c10425996503020b4aa478712a3a43","tid":1693873,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:34:31.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"fa18cbd6d4f2d35eceea41dc9c7a95cab7929fbe","tid":1693873,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"推二下，光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"731800cfeec7652b0aaf476433752412a73ec2c3","tid":1693873,"uid":94344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DD6cVmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDD6cVmt.jpg&h=73815b44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95ae63604494b8d0c46e6318bb76748f0ec402a9","tid":1693873,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:35:37.000Z","msg":"推三下，五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"0818dd5de7184cea5cdf3ed7d05007ffa333c829","tid":1693873,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"推四下，解散警隊，刻不容緩"},{"pid":"0f5ad99744eb042fb3f133296939b8122d1ee24d","tid":1693873,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:36:22.000Z","msg":"推五下，全港大罷工"},{"pid":"f1c1280dd9196249a36a254e0275469a9e9d4b45","tid":1693873,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"推六下，香港人反抗"},{"pid":"6dd356aa2e9e886c88e0c21bd2cd51c1e9d1a346","tid":1693873,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:37:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3f4d189050b4bea9baf92272aae8035b41c0cb","tid":1693873,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d735a1e730a4bdd3be7d4f56103a146a5703b83","tid":1693873,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:40:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a62350afd954379c7c147ef42e197139f11850e9","tid":1693873,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201